column5: Does anyone know of a good tackle shop in the general area of Highway 403 / Dundas (Hwy 5) area of Oakville?  Thanks, DW
I'm down the road from there, the only real option other than Canadian Tire or Wal Mart is LeBaron's at Dixie and Dundas in Mississauga OR JB's Fishing Depot at the 427/401 area.
Bronte Outdoors just moved to Mississauga, at Hurontario and Dundas...plus there is Angling Specialties at Confederation and Central Pkwy
